P(X = x) = \sum_{n=0}^\infty P(X = x\; {\rm and}\; N=n) = \sum_{n= 0}^\infty P(X = x|N=n)P(N=n)
P(X = x | N = n) = {n\choose x}p^x(1-p)^{n-x}
P(X=x) = \sum_{n=x}^\infty P(X=x|N=n)P(N=n) =  \sum_{n=x}^\infty {n\choose x}p^x(1-p)^{n-x}{r^ne^{-r}\over n!}.
P(X=x) = e^{-r}\sum_{n=x}^\infty {1\over x!(n-x)!}(rp)^x(r - rp)^{n-x} 
P(X=x) = e^{-r}\sum_{n=0}^\infty {1\over n!x!} (rp)^x(r-rp)^n =  {(rp)^xe^{-r}\over x!}\sum_{n=0}^\infty {(r-rp)^n\over n!}= {(rp)^xe^{-r}\over x!} e^{r-rp} = {(rp)^xe^{-rp}\over x!}.
